Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she saw Johan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll kill her after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have seen something I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him late one evening last year, \N that beautiful, blond haired boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kill those who see Johan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard three shots, got scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and started running.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure Dr. Tenma was hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the next day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:03:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the newspaper said that some guy named Junkers \N was shot three times and died instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy pulled the trigger, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to shoot me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you shoot me, you'll never get them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those pictures of Johan when he was \N a child that you've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think will happen if you shoot me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pictures will automatically be delivered to the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want those pictures, tell me where Tenma is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your legs are shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are acting pretty tough, but \N you can barely stand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an interesting woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Tenma doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is still a doctor, of course, but an unlicensed one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a guy who rose to second in command \N in this syndicate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the boss became afraid of \N him and tried to do him in...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but only managed to wound him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma is treating him in a mountain lodge...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...near Füssen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:41.05,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,109)\pos(363,314)}Men's Dining Table
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you been standing here for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost lunch time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the weather is great today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'm thinking of having lunch outdoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having lunch outdoors?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter, bring those plates over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your rehab is coming along nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting some sunshine will be good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma, you really saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:06:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You performed a perfect operation at \N such an old clinic in a country town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, your head was only grazed, and the other \N bullet passed directly through your leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your anterior tibial artery wasn't hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lucky, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch is served!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?  It's really good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Heckel my not look like \N a chef, his cooking is fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Chicken Marengo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic is in the sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the secret recipe from the 3 star \N restaurant "Le Petit Besson."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are always bragging.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids wouldn't understand such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you add a little soy sauce, I \N think it might be even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You put soy sauce on everything you eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you complaining about my cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dining table...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what it's like to sit at a dining table.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was willing to do almost anything for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I bother making all that money?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left home, made enemies of my brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and watched my wife and child get murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all I ever wanted was to sit at a table like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money can corrupt a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever heard this story?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five years ago, something similar to a bank...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that monopolized all black market \N money in Germany was established.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was one hell of an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We turned all the dirty money into clean, legit money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's money laundering, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The organization borrowed and \N traded like any normal bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It grew and amassed a huge fortune in only five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the head of this organization suddenly \N disappeared earlier this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think happened after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a huge fight over who would control the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the people died, and the organization collapsed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when all they needed to do was sit around \N a table like this and talk things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened to that leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who suddenly disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he was killed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive... somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be a student at some school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Student?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, don't be surprised when I tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor has it that when that man, no, that child \N started the organization five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he was only fifteen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen years old?  You have got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way a fifteen year old \N could do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, he managed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if he were experimenting on adults' \N behavior towards money...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like a kid crushing a line of ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:09:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where was this black market bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The organization was headquartered in Düsseldorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The top guy was always moving about \N and giving orders from various places.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where was he last, before he disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the details, but the people who were \N dazzled by the money all went to Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Doctor?  You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's invite the man at the \N bottom of the hill up for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but as my bodyguard, he's got a job to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They think you are already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you think they are still after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan on keeping the protection you've always had?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been with me a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, boy... Helmut...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So his name is Helmut!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, tell him that he doesn't need \N to be my bodyguard anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the last friend I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him to join me here at the table, \N and we'll talk about our future plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Helmut, lunch is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma is at the top of this hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to kill him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something has happened to Helmut \N at the bottom of the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmut is probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do know that someone is on his way up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Helmut...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to hurry up and get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him to hurry up and get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your leg is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he shooting from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!  If I leave you here, you will be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me, you have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta hide you in the woods...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all that, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...really didn't want to kill Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that guy may already be at the lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only road up to the lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been up and down this hill lots of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get up any other way because of the cliffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:15:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as long as we are here, that guy won't be able \N to get up there without going through us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That guy"?  Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's after Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Tenma?  Who are you lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Tenma's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, call me "miss," not "lady."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, quickly, go and tell Tenma to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But lady... I mean miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said before, I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you are bleeding pretty badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get Tenma, he will be able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you that Roberto is out to kill Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Tenma comes here, Roberto will \N get exactly what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we run away, you will bleed to death, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you not to call me "lady"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my friend.  How about you, la-- miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are his friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are protecting him even though you have been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like Tenma, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Tenma's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your eyes on your own side!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a whole lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you like about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do YOU like about him, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberto!  If you think you can keep hiding \N and toying with us, think again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, the pictures of Johan that you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will automatically be delivered to the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want those pictures, get your ass out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know his weak spot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may not fall for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't possibly be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma will soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not going to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes he will!  Tenma will...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't be coming to rescue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!  Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma, I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay right where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:17:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you come over here now, you'll be shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are his target!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This lady is your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got shot, and she is bleeding pretty badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My goal it to take you in alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to spend the rest of your life \N in prison, regretting what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regretting that you ever dumped me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk so loudly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!  Can you hear me, Dieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell where the shooter is from where you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea where he is hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you die...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't come...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't come...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten...ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are going to have lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are recovering very nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are well enough to have lunch \N outside in this fine weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who shot you is a top notch professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He estimated how difficult it would be \N to attack this lodge pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one route up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was pretty obvious that he couldn't come barging in...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...without knowing how much security I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he used you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.52,0:20:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have figured that the best way \N to get in was for a woman to drop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you betrayed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, when that happened, his plan failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he quickly left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was not hiding in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Chicken Marengo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it's any good, since \N I copied the recipe from someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are also lucky that you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...treated by Dr. Tenma, an outstanding physician.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.36,0:21:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seemed very interested in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Munich?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you also forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what it's like to eat at a dining table.
